      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1-generation Cayman S is a precision-engineered driver's tool featuring the 3.4L mid-mounted flat-six M97 engine. Power is delivered via a short-throw 6-speed manual transaxle, offering a mechanical connection that modern dual-clutch systems can't replicate. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its mid-engine architecture for a neutralized center of gravity and superb lateral grip. Technical highlights include VarioCam Plus valve timing for optimized torque delivery and a hydraulic power steering rack that provides genuine tactile feedback. Well-maintained with documented fluid intervals, the cooling system and AOS have been recently inspected to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
